comments: Hield (SAC) momentarily places his hand on Gordon's (HOU) side and he immediately removes it as he moves around Gordon off ball. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Wood (SAC) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Mitchell (SAC) briefly engages in marginal contact with Wood (HOU) following the pick.
Wood (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in Mitchell's (SAC) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Hield (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Wood's (HOU) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Metu (SAC) and Wood (HOU) briefly engage in marginal contact off ball prior to separating.
Mitchell (SAC) briefly places his hand on Wood's (HOU) front during the pick and he immediately removes it as both players disengage from the marginal contact.
Mitchell (SAC) makes contact to Porter Jr.'s (HOU) wrist and the contact affects his pass attempt.
Green (HOU) moves into Davis' (SAC) body following the steal and the contact affects his SQBR.
Wood (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in Mitchell's (SAC) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Davis (SAC) and Green (HOU) mutually engage in marginal contact prior to separating during the rebound.
Metu's (SAC) arm comes down and he makes contact to Gordon's (HOU) head during his driving shot attempt.

Gordon's (HOU) forearm collapses to his body and he absorbs he marginal body contact while moving along Barnes' (SAC) path during the drive. Gordon avoids making contact to Barnes' arm as he enters his upward shooting motion.
Metu (SAC) commits a take foul on Porter Jr. (HOU).
